Package maze

Class Maze.Coordinate

  • java.lang.Object
    • maze.Maze.Coordinate
  • Enclosing class:
    Maze
    public class Maze.Coordinate
extends java.lang.Object
    The inner class that describes a pair of coordinates(x, y). Both are 0-indexed; x=column left to right; y=row bottom to top. That makes the maze similar to a cartesian plane and sets calls to the array to (rowCount - y - 1, x) instead of (x, y)
